      <p class="fragment">
        <a href="https://chat.openai.com/chat">https://chat.openai.com/chat</a>
      </p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <p>Let's look at the</p>
      <ol>
        <li>Install day (fronter)<br />(including, what is it)</li>
        <li>JS Recap (fronter)</li>
        <li>Static Product Assignment (fronter)</li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://kea-alt-del.dk/t7/example-site/">Example site</a>
